    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>A review on June 3 about ''Twisted,'' by Laurie Halse Anderson, misstated the given name in two references for a character in ''Speak,'' another book by the same author. As noted elsewhere in the review, it is Melinda Sordino, not Miranda.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
